# patchwork
Patchwork is a package with the goal to make it ridiculously simple to combine separate ggplots into the same graphic.
patchwork is different from gridExtra::grid.arrange() and cowplot::plot_grid.

## Install
devtools::install_github("thomasp85/patchwork")

## [Simple document]
Find the simple guide on patchwork [here](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/patchwork/vignettes/patchwork.html)
